title: Seth Off-Air: Will Forte
description:
Stepping away from his desk in Studio 8G, Seth has an exclusive conversation with his friend and former Saturday Night Live colleague Will Forte.

Plus, Fred Armisen unexpectedly crashes the episode at 28:35.
